  FAMOUS PEOPLE
============================================================

Name:          Marie Curie
Lived:         1867 - 1934
Nationality:   Polish-French
Field:         Chemistry/Physics
Known For:     Radioactivity
Contribution:  First woman Nobel laureate; Nobel in two sciences; discovered radium and polonium
Quote:         "Nothing in life is to be feared, only to be understood."

Name:          Charles Darwin
Lived:         1809 - 1882
Nationality:   English
Field:         Biology
Known For:     Evolution by Natural Selection
Contribution:  On the Origin of Species; explained diversity of life on Earth
Quote:         "It is not the strongest that survives, but the most adaptable."

Name:          Tim Berners-Lee
Lived:         1955 - present
Nationality:   English
Field:         Computing
Known For:     World Wide Web
Contribution:  Invented the Web in 1989; gave it to the world for free
Quote:         "The web does not just connect machines, it connects people."

